---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro'
---

<MainLayout title='Tus apuntes de programación en un solo lugar'>
  <div
    class='rounded-lg border text-card-foreground shadow-sm bg-gray-800 border-gray-700 mb-8'
    data-id='9'
    data-v0-t='card'
  >
    <div class='flex flex-col space-y-1.5 p-6' data-id='10'>
      <h3 class='font-semibold tracking-tight text-2xl' data-id='11'>
        Contenido del Curso
      </h3><p class='text-sm text-gray-400' data-id='12'>
        Explora los fundamentos de la programación a través de varios lenguajes
      </p>
    </div><div class='p-6 pt-0' data-id='13'>
      <div dir='ltr' data-orientation='horizontal' class='w-full' data-id='14'>
        <div
          role='tablist'
          aria-orientation='horizontal'
          class='h-10 items-center justify-center rounded-md p-1 text-muted-foreground grid w-full grid-cols-3 bg-gray-700'
          data-id='15'
          tabindex='0'
          data-orientation='horizontal'
          style='outline: none;'
        >
          <button
            type='button'
            role='tab'
            aria-selected='true'
            aria-controls='radix-:r4:-content-python'
            data-state='active'
            id='radix-:r4:-trigger-python'
            class='inline-flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap rounded-sm px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium ring-offset-background transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 data-[state=active]:bg-background data-[state=active]:text-foreground data-[state=active]:shadow-sm'
            data-id='16'
            tabindex='0'
            data-orientation='horizontal'
            data-radix-collection-item=''>Python</button
          ><button
            type='button'
            role='tab'
            aria-selected='false'
            aria-controls='radix-:r4:-content-javascript'
            data-state='inactive'
            id='radix-:r4:-trigger-javascript'
            class='inline-flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap rounded-sm px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium ring-offset-background transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 data-[state=active]:bg-background data-[state=active]:text-foreground data-[state=active]:shadow-sm'
            data-id='17'
            tabindex='-1'
            data-orientation='horizontal'
            data-radix-collection-item=''>JavaScript</button
          ><button
            type='button'
            role='tab'
            aria-selected='false'
            aria-controls='radix-:r4:-content-java'
            data-state='inactive'
            id='radix-:r4:-trigger-java'
            class='inline-flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap rounded-sm px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium ring-offset-background transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 data-[state=active]:bg-background data-[state=active]:text-foreground data-[state=active]:shadow-sm'
            data-id='18'
            tabindex='-1'
            data-orientation='horizontal'
            data-radix-collection-item=''>Java</button
          >
        </div><div
          data-state='active'
          data-orientation='horizontal'
          role='tabpanel'
          aria-labelledby='radix-:r4:-trigger-python'
          id='radix-:r4:-content-python'
          tabindex='0'
          class='mt-2 ring-offset-background focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2'
          data-id='19'
          style=''
        >
          <div
            dir='ltr'
            class='relative overflow-hidden h-[400px] w-full rounded-md border border-gray-700 p-4'
            data-id='20'
            style='position: relative; --radix-scroll-area-corner-width: 0px; --radix-scroll-area-corner-height: 0px;'
          >
            <style>
              [data-radix-scroll-area-viewport] {
                scrollbar-width: none;
                -ms-overflow-style: none;
                -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
              }
              [data-radix-scroll-area-viewport]::-webkit-scrollbar {
                display: none;
              }
            </style><div
              data-radix-scroll-area-viewport=''
              class='h-full w-full rounded-[inherit]'
              style='overflow: hidden scroll;'
            >
              <div style='min-width: 100%; display: table;'>
                <h3 class='text-lg font-semibold mb-2' data-id='21'>
                  Ejemplo de Python
                </h3><pre
                  class='bg-gray-900 p-4 rounded-md overflow-x-auto'
                  data-id='22'><code class="text-sm font-mono" data-id="23"><span class="text-blue-400" data-id="24">def</span> <span class="text-green-400" data-id="25">saludar</span>(nombre):<span class="text-blue-400" data-id="26">print</span>(<span class="text-yellow-300" data-id="27">f"¡Hola, </span>nombre<span class="text-yellow-300" data-id="28">!"</span>)\n                      \n                      <span class="text-green-400" data-id="29">saludar</span>(<span class="text-yellow-300" data-id="30">"Mundo"</span>)<span class="text-gray-500" data-id="31"># Salida: ¡Hola, Mundo!</span></code></pre><p
                  class='mt-4'
                  data-id='32'
                >
                  Python es conocido por su sintaxis clara y legible, lo que lo
                  hace ideal para principiantes.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><div
          data-state='inactive'
          data-orientation='horizontal'
          role='tabpanel'
          aria-labelledby='radix-:r4:-trigger-javascript'
          id='radix-:r4:-content-javascript'
          tabindex='0'
          class='mt-2 ring-offset-background focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2'
          data-id='33'
          hidden=''
        >
        </div><div
          data-state='inactive'
          data-orientation='horizontal'
          role='tabpanel'
          aria-labelledby='radix-:r4:-trigger-java'
          id='radix-:r4:-content-java'
          tabindex='0'
          class='mt-2 ring-offset-background focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2'
          data-id='48'
          hidden=''
        >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
